      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual, the drivetrain remains tight with a recently serviced variable M differential lock. The high-revving DOHC valvetrain is in excellent health, and the dual-VANOS system has been professionally addressed to ensure optimal cam phasing. Structurally, the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced, maintaining chassis integrity during high-G cornering. While the aesthetics show minor age-appropriate patina, the mechanical fundamentals are robust, offering a pure, analog driving experience with precise throttle response and a balanced 50/50 weight distribution.",
